1
00:00:05,660 --> 00:00:08,356
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:08,429 --> 00:00:12,297
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:12,367 --> 00:00:16,360
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:16,704 --> 00:00:19,195
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19,273 --> 00:00:23,334
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:00:23,411 --> 00:00:27,370
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:28,850 --> 00:00:33,583
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34,288 --> 00:00:37,257
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:39,694 --> 00:00:41,787
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:42,530 --> 00:00:43,827
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:00:44,165 --> 00:00:46,725
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:54,776 --> 00:01:00,146
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:00,348 --> 00:01:01,508
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:01,582 --> 00:01:05,382
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:05,720 --> 00:01:10,919
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11,192 --> 00:01:12,523
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:12,593 --> 00:01:13,992
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:14,062 --> 00:01:20,331
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:33,965 --> 00:01:36,433
I'll show you there are walls

20
00:01:36,501 --> 00:01:40,164
which effort alone can
never break through.

21
00:01:49,614 --> 00:01:54,449
<i>Sakura Blossoms!</i>

22
00:02:17,509 --> 00:02:18,100
Huh?!

23
00:02:19,511 --> 00:02:22,412
Your Jutsu is indeed fast.

24
00:02:25,083 --> 00:02:29,884
But our Jutsu exceeds that
and is the speed of sound!

25
00:02:33,792 --> 00:02:34,622
Lee!

26
00:02:45,237 --> 00:02:46,795
<i>My left ear...</i>

27
00:02:49,207 --> 00:02:51,801
There's a little gimmick I have.

28
00:02:53,278 --> 00:02:58,682
Evading won't work!...
on my attacks.

29
00:03:01,186 --> 00:03:02,414
<i>What is he going to do?!</i>

30
00:03:06,391 --> 00:03:07,483
It's sound.

31
00:03:08,093 --> 00:03:12,189
Even though you evaded my fist,
sound assaulted you.

32
00:03:12,998 --> 00:03:13,930
<i>Sound?</i>

33
00:03:16,134 --> 00:03:20,127
Do you know what sound is
all about in the first place?

34
00:03:21,339 --> 00:03:22,328
Vibration?

35
00:03:22,774 --> 00:03:27,677
Correct. In other words,
hearing sounds means,

36
00:03:28,213 --> 00:03:33,412
that the eardrum is
catching vibrating air.

37
00:03:35,153 --> 00:03:40,591
And the human eardrum breaks
with sounds over 150 Mhz.

38
00:03:41,793 --> 00:03:47,254
Also, by assaulting the semicircular canal
which is located even deeper,

39
00:03:48,667 --> 00:03:51,227
I can make you totally lose balance.

40
00:03:56,675 --> 00:04:01,510
You won't be able to move your body
freely for sometime.

41
00:04:02,948 --> 00:04:07,078
Something old and tired
like Taijutsu don't work on us.

42
00:04:08,954 --> 00:04:11,479
Well, you were doing good
up to a certain point,

43
00:04:11,556 --> 00:04:13,717
but I brought forth my Jutsu.

44
00:04:14,159 --> 00:04:16,423
It's just not gonna work anymore.

45
00:04:19,497 --> 00:04:23,194
I freely manipulate ultrasonic waves
and air pressure,

46
00:04:23,602 --> 00:04:26,469
and have the power to
obliterate even boulders!

47
00:04:27,172 --> 00:04:28,605
Primary Lotus!

48
00:04:32,143 --> 00:04:34,236
I can send air into the ground

49
00:04:34,312 --> 00:04:37,213
and change the dirt into
a cushion as I please.

50
00:04:39,250 --> 00:04:42,447
It's different from
your silly Jutsu.

51
00:04:50,128 --> 00:04:51,390
<i>Blast it!</i>

52
00:04:58,637 --> 00:05:01,435
<i>Lee, it is all right to use</i>
<i>this Jutsu</i>

53
00:05:01,573 --> 00:05:05,134
<i>to protect someone precious.</i>

54
00:05:05,910 --> 00:05:09,437
<i>Protect...someone precious?</i>

55
00:05:14,719 --> 00:05:15,583
<i>In any case,</i>

56
00:05:15,654 --> 00:05:18,851
<i>I'm impressed that you</i>
<i>were able to master it, little man!</i>

57
00:05:21,192 --> 00:05:23,160
<i>You did it quite well, Lee!</i>

58
00:05:24,963 --> 00:05:26,726
<i>Damn it!</i>

59
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,194
Okay, then!

60
00:05:31,069 --> 00:05:32,058
Next is...

61
00:05:32,570 --> 00:05:33,502
You!

62
00:05:34,072 --> 00:05:34,663
Damn it!

63
00:05:34,973 --> 00:05:35,701
<i>He's coming!</i>

64
00:05:41,780 --> 00:05:42,474
What?!

65
00:05:42,547 --> 00:05:43,275
<i>No way!</i>

66
00:05:43,515 --> 00:05:44,311
<i>Lee!</i>

67
00:05:45,116 --> 00:05:46,014
Leaf...

68
00:05:46,084 --> 00:05:46,880
Hurricane!

69
00:05:48,586 --> 00:05:51,953
It looks like my earlier attack
is having an effect!

70
00:05:52,891 --> 00:05:55,018
I'm somewhat surprised...

71
00:05:55,660 --> 00:06:00,097
but there's not even a trace of
that flash of combo Taijutsu you showed!

72
00:06:06,604 --> 00:06:11,473
This arm amplifies sounds
from within to its maximum.

73
00:06:11,776 --> 00:06:13,767
It's a speaker of sorts!

74
00:06:15,647 --> 00:06:16,545
Lee!

75
00:06:17,615 --> 00:06:20,880
And the assault sound isn't limited
by the direction of my arm...

76
00:06:21,119 --> 00:06:25,852
it always converges on
the targeted prey by my Chakra!

77
00:06:26,491 --> 00:06:27,287
Lee!

78
00:06:32,130 --> 00:06:35,531
Now then...
The final blow.

79
00:06:36,101 --> 00:06:36,999
I won't let you!

80
00:06:41,539 --> 00:06:43,598
Oh, well.

81
00:06:45,176 --> 00:06:47,076
Hey, let's get outta here!

82
00:06:47,145 --> 00:06:49,443
Those guys are pretty dangerous!

83
00:06:50,415 --> 00:06:53,680
It looks like Sasuke and Naruto
are only unconscious, but...

84
00:06:54,352 --> 00:06:57,515
even that guy Lee's been
messed up and Sakura's alone.

85
00:06:57,922 --> 00:07:00,550
What're you gonna do, Ino?

86
00:07:01,659 --> 00:07:02,921
What do you mean?

87
00:07:04,329 --> 00:07:06,820
Well, Sakura's in deep trouble!

88
00:07:07,065 --> 00:07:08,430
You're all right with that?

89
00:07:08,700 --> 00:07:09,564
Huh?!

90
00:07:10,368 --> 00:07:12,928
You two were once close friends,
weren't you?

91
00:07:21,279 --> 00:07:22,507
<i>By the way...</i>

92
00:07:26,551 --> 00:07:29,952
<i>What Sakura, don't be so stiff!</i>

93
00:07:31,890 --> 00:07:32,879
<i>Well...</i>

94
00:07:33,825 --> 00:07:35,417
<i>Ino, I hear you also...</i>

95
00:07:36,828 --> 00:07:38,659
<i>What is it?</i>

96
00:07:40,698 --> 00:07:43,326
<i>...like Sasuke.</i>

97
00:07:53,812 --> 00:07:56,838
<i>Then, that means from now on,</i>

98
00:07:57,215 --> 00:07:58,739
<i>you and I are rivals.</i>

99
00:08:08,726 --> 00:08:12,958
<i>Why...why am I recalling things</i>
<i>from that time?</i>

100
00:08:14,032 --> 00:08:16,091
Hey, Ino!

101
00:08:17,135 --> 00:08:18,534
What're you gonna do?!

102
00:08:18,937 --> 00:08:21,997
I know, but there's nothing I can do!

103
00:08:22,073 --> 00:08:24,132
I can't heedlessly
go out there, can I?!

104
00:08:27,779 --> 00:08:29,576
<i>Even if I went out now...</i>

105
00:08:31,616 --> 00:08:34,278
<i>I'd be taken down without a doubt.</i>

106
00:08:36,287 --> 00:08:37,185
<i>I also...</i>

107
00:08:37,622 --> 00:08:38,554
<i>I also...!</i>

108
00:08:44,295 --> 00:08:47,594
<i>Air pressure!</i>
<i>The shurikens got bounced back?!</i>

109
00:08:57,775 --> 00:09:00,141
Your hair's shinier than mine.

110
00:09:00,712 --> 00:09:04,239
Hey! If you have time to worry
about your hair,

111
00:09:04,315 --> 00:09:05,577
you should practice!

112
00:09:06,251 --> 00:09:08,412
Getting all spiced up like a woman...

113
00:09:09,187 --> 00:09:15,183
Why don't you kill that Sasuke guy
right in front of this sexy bug, Zaku?

114
00:09:15,426 --> 00:09:17,257
Yeah! That sounds great!

115
00:09:17,862 --> 00:09:19,022
Hey hey...

116
00:09:19,631 --> 00:09:21,258
<i>I won't let you do such a thing!</i>

117
00:09:21,833 --> 00:09:22,765
Don't move!

118
00:09:25,670 --> 00:09:26,602
<i>Sakura.</i>

119
00:09:28,539 --> 00:09:33,067
<i>My body... It has no strength.</i>

120
00:09:46,424 --> 00:09:47,254
<i>I...</i>

121
00:09:49,494 --> 00:09:54,158
<i>Again...l'm just pulling everyone's feet!</i>

122
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,729
<i>I'm always being protected.</i>

123
00:09:58,736 --> 00:09:59,862
<i>It's so frustrating!</i>

124
00:10:02,707 --> 00:10:04,732
<i>This time for sure...</i>
<i>I had thought!</i>

125
00:10:06,110 --> 00:10:07,475
<i>This time for sure...</i>

126
00:10:08,012 --> 00:10:11,971
<i>I must protect people precious to me...</i>
<i>so I thought!</i>

127
00:10:17,655 --> 00:10:18,917
So...

128
00:10:19,090 --> 00:10:20,057
Let's do this!

129
00:10:36,941 --> 00:10:39,876
Hey! Sasuke and Naruto are
gonna get it, too!

130
00:10:43,181 --> 00:10:45,445
<i>W-What should I do?!</i>

131
00:10:53,858 --> 00:10:54,586
That's pointless!

132
00:10:56,394 --> 00:10:58,658
That won't work on me!

133
00:11:03,201 --> 00:11:04,498
What are you saying?

134
00:11:05,003 --> 00:11:05,662
Huh?

135
00:11:06,237 --> 00:11:06,965
What?!

136
00:11:38,415 --> 00:11:39,814
<i>I always...</i>

137
00:11:41,018 --> 00:11:43,987
<i>act as if I'm a full fledged Ninja.</i>

138
00:11:46,556 --> 00:11:49,821
<i>I always say that I like Sasuke.</i>

139
00:11:52,429 --> 00:11:55,694
<i>I always act like I know everything</i>
<i>and lecture Naruto.</i>

140
00:11:58,001 --> 00:12:02,961
<i>I always just...watch them from behind.</i>

141
00:12:06,710 --> 00:12:07,802
<i>And yet...</i>

142
00:12:09,112 --> 00:12:10,374
<i>Tazuna, get back!</i>

143
00:12:20,123 --> 00:12:21,112
<i>Get back!</i>

144
00:12:29,967 --> 00:12:31,025
<i>Now then...</i>

145
00:12:32,569 --> 00:12:33,934
<i>Let's get wild!</i>

146
00:12:44,147 --> 00:12:47,173
<i>This is the only way to</i>
<i>take him down!</i>

147
00:12:47,918 --> 00:12:49,112
<i>Sasuke!</i>

148
00:13:01,732 --> 00:13:03,791
<i>Here it is!</i>

149
00:13:05,969 --> 00:13:09,996
<i>Those two always covered</i>
<i>my back and fought for me.</i>

150
00:13:18,782 --> 00:13:23,515
<i>Lee, you say that you like me...</i>

151
00:13:25,856 --> 00:13:27,483
<i>I'll protect you until I die!</i>

152
00:13:32,796 --> 00:13:34,195
<i>Primary Lotus!</i>

153
00:13:37,067 --> 00:13:38,364
<i>With me at your back...</i>

154
00:13:38,735 --> 00:13:40,999
<i>you risked your life and</i>
<i>fought for me.</i>

155
00:13:42,506 --> 00:13:45,873
<i>I have a feeling that you taught me...</i>

156
00:13:49,613 --> 00:13:51,012
Sakura!

157
00:13:52,282 --> 00:13:53,647
Sakura!

158
00:13:54,618 --> 00:13:55,778
Humph!

159
00:13:57,120 --> 00:14:00,112
<i>I want to be like all of you!</i>

160
00:14:05,529 --> 00:14:06,553
<i>This time...</i>

161
00:14:07,330 --> 00:14:08,820
<i>I want all of you...</i>

162
00:14:11,001 --> 00:14:12,628
<i>to watch me...</i>

163
00:14:14,805 --> 00:14:16,329
<i>...from behind!</i>

164
00:14:21,078 --> 00:14:21,976
<i>Sakura?</i>

165
00:14:23,680 --> 00:14:24,510
Sakura...

166
00:14:27,717 --> 00:14:28,615
Kin! Kill her!

167
00:14:32,322 --> 00:14:34,051
<i>Huh! That sign...</i>

168
00:14:40,697 --> 00:14:41,891
<i>Substitution Jutsu!</i>

169
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:46,169
<i>On the right, huh?</i>
<i>You think I'm a fool?</i>

170
00:14:46,436 --> 00:14:48,370
<i>With such a simple and basic Ninjutsu...</i>

171
00:14:48,438 --> 00:14:50,463
<i>you think you can come at me?!</i>

172
00:14:51,675 --> 00:14:52,733
Kin, get out of the way!

173
00:14:54,778 --> 00:14:55,676
Useless!

174
00:14:56,646 --> 00:15:00,343
<i>Air pressure 100 percent,</i>
<i>ultrasonic waves 0%, output...</i>

175
00:15:01,151 --> 00:15:02,516
<i>Is that all you can do?</i>

176
00:15:03,086 --> 00:15:04,246
Slicing Sound Wave!

177
00:15:07,057 --> 00:15:07,751
<i>You're easy to spot...</i>

178
00:15:08,024 --> 00:15:08,752
<i>You're above!</i>

179
00:15:11,862 --> 00:15:15,491
I've said it two or three times that
that won't work!

180
00:15:16,233 --> 00:15:18,167
This is enough... for you!

181
00:15:22,172 --> 00:15:23,503
Where next?

182
00:15:25,308 --> 00:15:25,797
Huh?!

183
00:15:26,610 --> 00:15:27,542
What.?!

184
00:15:28,678 --> 00:15:31,078
<i>This time...it's not a substitution!</i>

185
00:15:41,391 --> 00:15:42,858
Get off me! Hey!

186
00:15:47,731 --> 00:15:48,755
<i>Sakura...</i>

187
00:15:58,408 --> 00:16:02,139
<i>You're always being called</i>
<i>"Billboard Brow" and being picked on.</i>

188
00:16:05,882 --> 00:16:06,906
<i>Who're you?</i>

189
00:16:07,184 --> 00:16:11,712
<i>I'm called Ino Yamanaka.</i>
<i>How'bout you?</i>

190
00:16:12,989 --> 00:16:16,390
<i>I'm...Sakura.</i>

191
00:16:16,693 --> 00:16:22,222
<i>Huh? I can't hear you.</i>
<i>Say it louder.</i>

192
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:25,627
<i>Sakura Haruno!</i>

193
00:16:26,870 --> 00:16:29,532
<i>Huh, I see.</i>

194
00:16:29,906 --> 00:16:32,170
<i>You have a wide forehead.</i>

195
00:16:32,342 --> 00:16:34,776
<i>So, Billboard Brow, huh...?</i>

196
00:16:36,413 --> 00:16:39,439
<i>That's why you hide</i>
<i>your forehead with your bangs.</i>

197
00:16:39,616 --> 00:16:41,140
<i>Like a ghost...</i>

198
00:16:48,291 --> 00:16:49,815
<i>Sakura, was it?</i>

199
00:16:50,227 --> 00:16:51,057
<i>Uh huh...</i>

200
00:16:53,330 --> 00:16:55,525
<i>Come back here tomorrow.</i>

201
00:16:56,333 --> 00:16:58,324
<i>I'll give you something nice.</i>

202
00:16:58,802 --> 00:16:59,598
<i>Huh?</i>

203
00:17:01,404 --> 00:17:02,894
Damn, let g

204
00:17:05,041 --> 00:17:09,273
<i>See! You look cuter like this, Sakura!</i>

205
00:17:09,980 --> 00:17:11,607
<i>I'll give you that ribbon.</i>

206
00:17:11,948 --> 00:17:15,247
<i>T-Thanks.</i>

207
00:17:16,653 --> 00:17:17,312
<i>But...</i>

208
00:17:17,687 --> 00:17:18,915
<i>But what?</i>

209
00:17:20,190 --> 00:17:21,088
<i>My forehead...</i>

210
00:17:22,359 --> 00:17:26,693
<i>You hide it, so people make</i>
<i>more fun of you, you know?!</i>

211
00:17:27,464 --> 00:17:31,332
<i>You have a cute face Sakura,</i>
<i>so you should be more confident!</i>

212
00:17:31,401 --> 00:17:32,425
<i>More confident!</i>

213
00:17:33,503 --> 00:17:34,595
<i>Ino...</i>

214
00:17:38,541 --> 00:17:42,841
<i>Hey, who's that?</i>
<i>Who's she, Ino?</i>

215
00:17:43,079 --> 00:17:44,546
<i>Her name's Sakura.</i>

216
00:17:44,881 --> 00:17:47,076
<i>Hey, say hello!</i>

217
00:17:49,252 --> 00:17:50,014
<i>Hello...</i>

218
00:17:54,357 --> 00:17:55,881
<i>Listen everybody! Listen!</i>

219
00:17:56,826 --> 00:18:01,820
<i>There's someone I like!</i>
<i>Who do you think it is?</i>

220
00:18:02,065 --> 00:18:03,396
<i>Hurry up and tell us!</i>

221
00:18:04,267 --> 00:18:06,428
<i>Don't say it's Sasuke?</i>

222
00:18:06,970 --> 00:18:09,803
<i>Huh? Why'd you know?</i>

223
00:18:09,906 --> 00:18:11,601
<i>What're you talking about?</i>

224
00:18:11,708 --> 00:18:15,166
<i>Sasuke's really popular,</i>
<i>he's the most popular!</i>

225
00:18:15,312 --> 00:18:17,075
<i>Huh? Is that so?</i>

226
00:18:17,914 --> 00:18:21,975
<i>Oh no! I'll have a lot of rivals.</i>
<i>What should I do?!</i>

227
00:18:22,852 --> 00:18:27,687
<i>Hey, Ino! Sakura's been upbeat lately!</i>

228
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:32,526
<i>She's just acting brave</i>
<i>and romping around!</i>

229
00:18:36,700 --> 00:18:42,605
<i>Ino! I've heard Sasuke</i>
<i>likes girls with long hair.</i>

230
00:18:43,073 --> 00:18:49,205
<i>...likes girls with long hair.</i>
<i>...likes girls with long hair.</i>

231
00:18:49,612 --> 00:18:50,601
<i>Sakura...</i>

232
00:18:52,048 --> 00:18:55,609
<i>I've heard you like Sasuke, too, Ino.</i>

233
00:18:57,387 --> 00:18:59,753
<i>From now on, we're rivals.</i>

234
00:19:04,260 --> 00:19:06,922
<i>Your hair. It's grown quite a bit.</i>

235
00:19:07,797 --> 00:19:08,661
<i>Ino...</i>

236
00:19:09,399 --> 00:19:10,297
<i>Why...</i>

237
00:19:12,135 --> 00:19:15,832
<i>Why are you on the</i>
<i>same team as Sasuke?!</i>

238
00:19:16,773 --> 00:19:19,674
<i>I will not lose anymore... to you, Ino!</i>

239
00:19:20,510 --> 00:19:27,109
<i>Me too! I won't lose to you, Sakura.</i>
<i>No matter what!</i>

240
00:19:44,067 --> 00:19:45,159
<i>...Sakura!</i>

241
00:19:50,807 --> 00:19:51,569
<i>I will...</i>

242
00:19:52,041 --> 00:19:53,201
<i>I will...</i>

243
00:20:08,491 --> 00:20:09,788
Give it up!

244
00:20:10,727 --> 00:20:11,921
It's really bad...

245
00:20:13,963 --> 00:20:15,328
Hey, Ino!

246
00:20:19,235 --> 00:20:22,170
<i>I must...protect everyone!</i>

247
00:20:23,606 --> 00:20:24,971
You punk!

248
00:20:38,421 --> 00:20:39,149
Huh?

249
00:20:40,690 --> 00:20:44,251
Huh! More strange ones.

250
00:20:44,894 --> 00:20:46,020
Ino?

251
00:20:49,065 --> 00:20:53,092
Sakura! I promised
I wouldn't lose to you, didn't I?!

252
00:21:05,662 --> 00:21:10,395
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

253
00:21:10,500 --> 00:21:18,600
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

254
00:21:19,676 --> 00:21:28,209
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

255
00:21:28,819 --> 00:21:36,521
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

256
00:21:37,928 --> 00:21:43,457
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

257
00:21:43,533 --> 00:21:47,299
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

258
00:21:47,371 --> 00:21:50,932
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

259
00:21:51,408 --> 00:21:59,816
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

260
00:22:00,217 --> 00:22:05,280
<i>when you want to cry, and you want to run away</i>

261
00:22:05,355 --> 00:22:09,758
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

262
00:22:09,926 --> 00:22:13,589
<i>Just sing.</i>

263
00:22:13,897 --> 00:22:18,994
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

264
00:22:19,136 --> 00:22:21,263
<i>The two are one</i>

265
00:22:21,371 --> 00:22:27,640
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

266
00:22:28,245 --> 00:22:33,239
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

267
00:22:37,363 --> 00:22:39,923
Wow! This is Ino team's battle?!

268
00:22:40,466 --> 00:22:42,366
What a formation based on calculations!

269
00:22:42,835 --> 00:22:44,462
I hate to admit it,
but they're strong!

270
00:22:45,204 --> 00:22:49,766
Even the Sound Village ones
would be no match for them!

271
00:22:50,243 --> 00:22:52,074
We'll protect Sasuke...

272
00:22:52,645 --> 00:22:54,806
Huh?! What's this feeling?

273
00:22:55,982 --> 00:22:57,973
Next episode: " Battle Formation:
Ino Shika Cho!"

274
00:22:59,719 --> 00:23:01,949
What in the world is going on?!
